<H3> <TI>   Party Delegation Received by Chinese Counterpart </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Party Delegation Received by Chinese Counterpart </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2404135094 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 23 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2404135094 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] A China party official said China attaches great 
importance to its traditional friendship with Vietnam. At a 
reception given to a Vietnamese party delegation led by 
Secretary of the party Central Committee Mr. Hong Ha in Beijing 
on Friday, Mr. Qiao Shi said China also attaches importance to 
the improvement of neighborliness and cooperation between the 
two countries. He stressed that, in the present world 
situation, what is important to the two countries is to maintain 
contact and regular exchanges of views. 

</TEXT>

