<H3> <TI>   KR Fighting Continues in Battambang, Siem Reap </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    KR Fighting Continues in Battambang, Siem Reap </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Further Success at Pailin </H4>

<F P=102> BK2304104694 (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia in Cambodian 2330 GMT 22 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2304104694 </F>
<F P=104>  (Clandestine) Voice of the Great National Union 
Front of Cambodia </F>

<F P=105>  Cambodian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] On 21 and 22 April, we continued to mop up the 
invading forces in the east. We seized two T-54 tanks, three 
armored carriers, a scout car, two BM multiple rocket launchers, 
a 155-mm cannon, two trucks carrying ammunition, two tankers, a 
truck loaded with BM rockets, a Russian-made jeep, and 300 
assorted armaments. 

</TEXT>

