<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Koreans in China Denounce `War Provocation' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Koreans in China Denounce `War Provocation' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2304110694 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1025 GMT 23 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2304110694 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 23 (KCNA) -- The Beijing, Shanghai, 
Tianjin, Jinan, Qingdao, Taiyuan, Wuhan and Wulanhaote branches 
of the central and southern area chapter of the headquarters of 
Koreans in China of the National Alliance for the Country's 
Reunification [Pomminnyon] issued a joint statement April 7 
denouncing the new war provocation moves of the U.S. 
imperialists and the South Korean puppet clique. 
  The statement charged that the "civilian"-veiled traitorous 
clique of Kim Yong-sam, a heinous warmanic, as if the deployment 
of over 1,000 pieces of U.S. nuclear weapons in South Korea, 
were not enough, is begging for the resumption of Team Spirit 
joint military maneuvers and deploying Patriot missiles in a bid 
to unleash a nuclear war in conspiracy with U.S. imperialism. 
  The statement said: "The branches of the central and 
southern 
area chapter bitterly denounce the reckless arms buildup of the 
U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppet clique as a wanton 
challenge to the nation's desire for peace and denuclearization 
of the Korean peninsula and an unpardonable act to exterminate 
the nation." 
  It declared they would intensify the anti-U.S., anti-war and 
anti-nuke struggle in order to save the nation from the danger 
of nuclear war, in hearty response to the 10-point programme of 
the great unity of the whole nation, and courageously turn out 
in the noble cause of defending Korean-style socialism centred 
on the masses and achieving the independent and peaceful 
reunification. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

