<H3> <TI>   Vietnamese Party Delegation Continues Visit </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Vietnamese Party Delegation Continues Visit </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    WPK Hosts Reception </H4>

<F P=102> SK2404091394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0819 GMT 24 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2404091394 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, April 24 (KCNA) -- The Central Committee 
[C.C.] of the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] hosted a reception 
at the Mansudae Assembly Hall Saturday for a delegation of the 
Communist Party of Vietnam on a visit to Korea. 
  Invited there were the members of the delegation headed by 
Secretary of the Central Committee of the Party Hong Ha and 
Vietnamese Ambassador to Korea Duong Chinh Thuc. 
  Speaking at the reception, Secretary of the C.C., the WPK 
Hwang Chang-yop said that mutual visits between the two parties 
are a clear token of the common will of the two parties to 
support and cooperate closely with each other in accomplishing 
the cause of socialism. 
  He said that the Korean people rejoice as over their own 
over 
the achievements made by the fraternal Vietnamese people and 
sincerely wish them new successes in their future efforts to 
implement the resolution of the conference of the party. 
  "The friendship between the two parties and two peoples is 
noble friendship nursed by the respected leader of our people 
President Kim Il-song and the respected leader of the Vietnamese 
people Comrade Ho Chi Minh in the anti-imperialist common 
struggle long ago. Our party and people will support and 
closely cooperate with the fraternal Vietnamese party and people 
in the cause of socialism in the future too," he stated. 
  Speaking next, head of the delegation Hong Ha said: 
  "The Korean people have registered great achievements in the 
cause of socialist construction under the leadership of the 
Workers' Party of Korea headed by respected President Kim 
Il-song and the sagacious guidance of Comrade Kim Chong-il." 
  Saying that the Vietnamese people always rejoice as over 
their own over the achievements made by the Korean people in 
socialist construction and have actively supported the 
independent and peaceful reunification of Korea, he declared his 
party would make beneficial efforts to further develop the 
friendly relations between the two parties and two peoples. 

</TEXT>

