<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Meeting of Coal Industry Functionaries Held </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Meeting of Coal Industry Functionaries Held </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Hong Song-nam Delivers Report </H4>

<F P=102> SK2204135194 Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 0100 GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK2204135194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang Korean Central Broadcasting Network 
in Korean 0100 GMT 21 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=105> Korean </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] Comrade Hong Song-nam delivered a report to the 
national meeting of functionaries of the coal industry. The 
speaker stated that the national meeting of functionaries of the 
coal industry began at an exciting time when all party members 
and workers were accelerating an all-out march to implement the 
party's revolutionary strategies in hearty response to the great 
leader Comrade Kim Il-song's New Year's address for this year 
and the decision of the 21st plenary meeting of the sixth party 
Central Committee. He mentioned that the dear leader Comrade 
Kim Chong-il, who had always paid deep attention to the 
development of the coal industry, expressed his confidence and 
love by convening this meeting and sending a congratulatory 
message signed by the party Central Committee to the meeting. 
  The speaker stressed that the history of our country's 
socialist economic construction, which had been carried out 
along the single road of self-reliance under the banner of the 
chuche idea, started with the work of developing the coal 
industry in the country and that it was a proud history of 
victory and based on the achievements from this work we expanded 
the scale of the people's economy, improved the structure of the 
branches [pumungujo] of the people's economy, and built a 
powerful self-reliant national economy in which coal is used as 
a fuel and resource and a source of power. 
  He also said that when he was leading the work of building a 
new fatherland after the liberation, the great leader described 
the coal industry as a leading sector of the people's economy 
and presented a creative idea of developing this industry ahead 
of other sectors. [passage omitted] 
  The speaker also said that no force can stop our people who, 
filled with confidence and optimism, were marching along the 
single road of chuche while upholding the great leader and the 
dear comrade leader on the vanguard of the revolution. He 
stressed a need for all to achieve single-hearted unity around 
the party and the leader [suryong], bring new turns in coal 
production, and, thus, contribute to defending and maintaining 
socialism of our own style and further glorifying it. 
  The meeting hall was filled with the participants' resolve 
to 
thoroughly implement the tasks presented by the great leader's 
New Year's address for this year and the congratulatory message 
of the Workers' Party of Korea Central Committee and, thus, 
repay the party's trust and expectations with loyal deeds. 
Then, a congratulatory group of the Korean Children's Union 
came into the meeting hall and read a congratulatory message. 
  Following this, debates took place at the meeting. [passage 
omitted] 

</TEXT>

