<H4>    Message From Bolshevik Party </H4>

<F P=102> SK2504054194 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0459 GMT 25 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2504054194 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


