support to the peoples struggling for defence of their freedom 
and independence against imperialism and for the victory of 
socialism in our planet. 
  The All-Union Bolshevik Communist Party highly appreciates 
the role of the great leader Comrade Kim Il-song and you, the 
dear leader, and the Workers' Party of Korea in the publication 
of the Pyongyang declaration which opened up a new phase for the 
unity of the world communist movement and revolutionary movement. 

