<F P=100> North Korea </F>
<H3> <TI>   Further on Events Marking KPA Anniversary </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Further on Events Marking KPA Anniversary </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Article Recalls Kim Chong-il Work </H4>

<F P=102> SK2404092394 Pyongyang KCNA in English 0830 GMT 24 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2404092394 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Great Work Which Enables KPA To Fully Discharge its </F>
Mission and Duty" -- KCNA headline] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, April 24 (KCNA) -- NODONG SINMUN today 
carries a signed article on the lapse of ten years since the 
dear leader Comrade Kim Chong-il published his famous work "The 
People's Army Must Defend Its Leader and Party, Political System 
and Motherland With Its Life". 
  In his speech at the banquet arranged on the 52nd [as 
received] anniversary of the foundation of the Korean People's 
Army [KPA], Comrade Kim Chong-il, supreme commander, put forward 
tasks to build up the People's Army more firmly and increase its 
might, declaring it is the revolutionary Armed Forces of the 
party and its mission is to guarantee the revolutionary cause of 
the party with arms. 
  The daily in the article titled "It is Duty of the People's 
Army to Defend the Party and the Leader and the Political System 
and the Motherland With Its Life" says: 
  It is a famous work greatly conducive to Army building and 
the accomplishment of the revolutionary cause as it gives 
answers to all problems arising in strengthening the People's 
Army into the Army of the leader and the party. 
  The idea, theory and policy for building the Army and 
strengthening it, which are specified in the work, have 
displayed great vitality through practices and their validity 
and attraction fully demonstrated. 
  The validity and vitality of the work are clearly 
manifested, 
above all, in that the backbone ranks of the People's Army have 
been built up more firmly and the whole Army is filled with the 
unshakable determination to be intensively loyal to comrade 
supreme commander and to share the destiny with him. 
  Today the KPA's backbone ranks have grown markedly and their 
role in Army building and military activities is constantly 
increasing. 
  Unshakable in its determination to be intensively loyal to 
General Kim Chong-il, supreme commander, our People's Army has 
become invincible ranks firmly defending the party and the 
leader, the socialist motherland without vacillation in any 
storm. 
  The validity and vitality of the work are also expressed 
evidently in that the whole Army has become matchless ranks in 
which an iron discipline of remaining intensively loyal to 
comrade supreme commander has been established. 
  The intention and plan of comrade supreme commander are 
quickly and correctly conveyed to each soldier and the whole 
Army breathes the same breath with him and thinks and acts as he 
intends. This is the proud looks of the Korean People's Army. 
  The KPA now is an ideological united body of true 
revolutionary soldiers who are struggling with the idea of 
General Kim Chong-il, supreme commander, as its unshakable faith. 
  Its validity and vitality are manifested next in that the 
KPA 
is fully demonstrating its might as a matchless Army well 
prepared militarily and technically. 
  It is displaying its honor as strong, revolutionary armed 
forces equipped with both modern offensive and defensive means. 
  The present reality shows that a revolutionary Army can have 
invincible might and demonstrate its honor as glorious 
revolutionary Armed Forces which reliably defend their party and 
leader, the socialist motherland and the gains of the revolution 
when it has a genius of military arts and ever-victorious, 
iron-willed brilliant commander as its supreme commander, the 
paper stresses. 

</TEXT>

