<H3> <TI>   Kim Chong-il Praised for `Rare Military Wisdom' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Kim Chong-il Praised for `Rare Military Wisdom' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK2304215094 Pyongyang KCNA in English 1511 GMT 23 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> SK2304215094 </F>
<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> ["Outstanding Military Strategist" -- KCNA headline] </F>
  [Text] Pyongyang, April 23 (KCNA) -- Dear Comrade Kim 
Chong-il is a great military strategist and iron-willed 
brilliant commander possessed of rare military wisdom, matchless 
grit and distinguished commanding art. 
  He has published many works including "Let Us Strengthen the 
People's Army into Matchless Ranks" to give a comprehensive 
answers to all the theoretical and practical questions arising 
in building revolutionary Armed Forces, and has strengthened and 
developed the Korean People's Army [KPA] into invincible Armed 
Forces with energetic guidance. 
  It is the greatest feat performed by Comrade Kim Chong-il in 
the great work of Army building that he has trained the KPA into 
loyal and filial Armed Forces defending the party and the 
leader, the country and people with their lives. 
  He has attached particular importance to the singlehearted 
unity of the whole Army based on the idea of the leader in 
increasing its combat capabilities. He put forward a new policy 
of modelling the whole Army on the chuche idea to this end. 
  And he trained the whole Army into ranks with steel-like 
discipline that act as one on the orders and instructions of the 
party, ranks singleheartedly united in ideology and purpose and 
in morality and sense of obligation, with his tireless energetic 
guidance. The integral whole of complete unity in ideology and 
purpose, the community of destiny, that shares the destiny and 
bitters and sweets in the struggle for the country and people -- 
this is the looks of the KPA that has grown up under the loving 
care of the great brilliant commander. 
  Comrade Kim Chong-il has wisely led the work of building a 
powerful self-reliant national defence industry to strengthen 
and develop the KPA into an invincible Army. 
  He, with a deep insight into the features of modern warfare, 
indicated the direction and ways of building the self-reliant 
national defence industry and solved all problems with 
never-ceasing trips of on-the-spot guidance. 
  Thus, the KPA has been strengthened into invincible ranks 
equipped with modern offensive and defensive means. 
  Another great feat performed by Comrade Kim Chong-il in the 
great work of Army building is that he has made sure that the 
beautiful traits of Army-civilian unity is fully displayed 
throughout the country so that the Army and the people may help 
each other, and that the arming of the entire people and the 
fortification of the whole country have been completed. 
  In Korea, under his outstanding guidance and politics of 
love, the Army and people are united by blood ties like one 
family and the whole country has turned into an impregnable 
fortress which no formidable enemy can provoke. 
  The iron will, grit and distinguished commanding art of 
Comrade Kim Chong-il instill deep conviction of victory in the 
revolution and fighting spirit into the Korean people. 
  In early March last year a touch-and-go crisis was created 
on 
the Korean peninsula owing to the adventurous aggressive war 
rackets of the U.S. imperialists and the South Korean puppet 
clique. Progressive mankind of the world was deeply concerned 
over it. At that time, Comrade Kim Chong-il proclaimed a 
semi-war state to the whole country, entire people and whole 
Army and saw to it that a decisive statement on the withdrawal 
of the DPRK from NPT [Nuclear Nonproliferation Treaty] was 
issued in the wake of it. 
  And he turned the whole party, the entire people and the 
whole Army into a powerful combat force and the Korean people 
rose up like a mountain in hearty response to the call of the 
illustrious leader. The enemies trembled with fear. 
  This was how peace on the Korean peninsula and the rest of 
Asia was defended. 
  "We will win because General Kim Chong-il, an iron-willed 
brilliant commander, is leading us"--this is the unshakable will 
and faith of the Korean people and the People's Army officers 
and soldiers. 

</TEXT>

