<H3> <TI>   President: Country Ready for ASEAN Membership </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    President: Country Ready for ASEAN Membership </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2704152794 Hanoi VNA in English 1431 GMT 27 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> BK2704152794 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi VNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Hanoi vna april 27 -- 'Vietnam is prepared to become 
full member of ASEAN to further promote the friendship and 
multifaceted cooperation with all countries, through 
contributing to pace, stability and development in the region', 
President Le Duc Anh told ASEAN Secretary General Ajit Singh 
during his official visit to Indonesia. 
  In his courtesy visit paid to the Vietnamese Leader in 
Jakarta today, Mr. A. Singh expressed his pleasure at Vietnam's 
new development in national construction. He informed President 
Anh of ASEAN's willingness to extend full membership to Vietnam. 
  President Anh thanked ASEAN member countries and Mr. Singh 
himself for their goodwill towards Vietnam. 

</TEXT>

