<F P=100> Vietnam </F>
<H3> <TI>   Socioeconomic Growth Expected in Quang Ninh </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Socioeconomic Growth Expected in Quang Ninh </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK2604134294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network in Vietnamese 
1100 GMT 25 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK2604134294 </F>
<F P=104>  Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Network </F>
<F P=105>  Vietnamese </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The party committee, people's council, people's 
committee, and Fatherland Front Committee of Ha Long town held a 
grand meeting at Hon Gai Stadium in Quang Ninh Province on the 
morning of 25 April to make public a government decree on 
establishing Ha Long town under Quang Ninh Province. 
  Comrade Nguyen Binh Giang, member of the party Central 
Committee and secretary of the Quang Ninh Province party 
committee; Comrade Pham The Duyet, secretary of the Hanoi 
municipal party committee; and representatives of various 
central-level organs and of many provinces and cities nationwide 
attended the meeting. 
  The meeting began with a street parade with the 
participation 
of tens of thousands of people, and was followed by a ceremonial 
reading of the government decree on the establishment of Ha Long 
town under the administration of Hon Gai city in Quang Ninh 
Province. 
  The birth of Ha Long town will further spur the 
socioeconomic 
growth of Quang Ninh Province as well as of Bac Bo delta and is 
a significant event for the entire country. 
  The grand meeting held to make public the government decree 
on the establishment of Ha Long town concluded with a variety 
show performed by thousands of youths and teenagers which marked 
the beginning of the first cultural and sports festival of Ha 
Long town. 

</TEXT>

